Babu Help Menu
Syntax: ~mute <users...> [time_and_reason]
Mute users.
<users...> is a space separated list of usernames, ID's, or mentions. [time_and_reason] is the time to mute for and reason. Time is any valid time length such as 30 minutes or 2 days. If nothing is provided the mute will use the set default time or indefinite if not set. Examples: ~mute @member1 @member2 spam 5 hours ~mute @member1 3 days
Type ~help <command> for more info on a command. You can also type ~help <category> for more info on a category.
